STATE of Louisiana
v.
George H. PONSELL, Jr. NO. 2018-KH-1189 Supreme Court of Louisiana. September 28, 2018

WRIT NOT CONSIDERED. Petitioner has not demonstrated that he sought review in the court(s) below before filing in this Court nor shown the "extraordinary circumstances" that would justify bypassing *921that level of review. La.S.ct.R. X § 5(b).
